OL,5, The number of people leaving the       
OL,6, workforce due to long term sickness is 
OL,7, at its highest since the 1990s, a      
OL,8, report suggests.                       
OL,10,FAdults economically inactive due to    
OL,11,Fill-health rose from 2.1m in July 2019 
OL,12,Fto a peak of 2.8m in October 2023, said
OL,13,Fthe Resolution Foundation.             
OL,15,FIt is the "longest sustained rise"     
OL,16,Fsince 1994-1998, when records began.   
OL,18,FThe government said its recent Budget  
OL,19,Fmeasures are estimated to boost the    
OL,20,Flabour force by 300,000 workers.       
